Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是桔梗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了粥过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗你以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再照顾我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到姐姐偷偷救了一个\N叫鬼蜘蛛的强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能跟犬夜叉说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依那家伙的个性\N他一定会吃醋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  助我一臂之力好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然没头没脑的这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人\N来拜托我去消灭妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也有点招架不住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的报酬可是很高的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  往你那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  那是它的本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你姐姐手上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个叫做\N四魂之玉的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道四魂之玉的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那些坏蛋\N全都盯着那个四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那个玉\N越是沾染上仇恨的鲜血就会变得越邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姐姐会把四魂之玉净化\N不会让它变邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗总是装得一本正经\N圣洁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人真想看看\N那个女人慌乱时候的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到这一点\N我就越来越兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛说了那样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  老实说我好讨厌他喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕这辈子\N都只能躺在那里不能动弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初桔梗姐姐是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从姐姐的这种仁慈之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么感觉到了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.66,0:04:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在樱花树下\N站得太久的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的气息就会变得不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为这樱花的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你\N跟我上次见到的时候完全变了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的灵力怎么变得这么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只怕那些妖怪\N还有魑魅魍魉之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会突破你设下的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说\N是你释放出这些妖怪咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然真的被男人迷了心窍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方就是那个\N无法完全进化的半妖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把四魂之玉交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我代替你\N来净化那颗四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕你没有这个本事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想取你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的邪恶想法\N把我们招引过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我听听看\N你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一个\N能够自由活动的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能让四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和桔梗完完全全的属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过交换条件是\N必须把你的灵魂交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到\N我这个腐朽的灵魂还有点用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对地\N给我身体还有力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进步了很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来对付那些\N特别难缠难以战胜的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被射中的妖怪会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将永远沉睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要唤醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有当射箭的人发自内心\N希望这个妖怪苏醒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才可以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要特别小心这棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这棵神木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这棵树叫做时代树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说拥有穿越时空的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时代树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被封印在这棵树上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个妖怪的肉体就不会腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这么多的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没有注意到\N这么强大的邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  妖怪们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  把四魂之玉抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉将会赐予你们\N这个世界上最强大的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们将会成为最强大的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把巫女桔梗杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来得太晚了  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的灵力真的变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血刃飞爪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼的眼睛怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子  是我害了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我这个姐姐太不争气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要那么自责了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟人家打架本来就常常\N会有这种意外发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有战斗的话\N你就不再是你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前你也问过这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想放弃战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想放弃战斗\N然后试着当平凡的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本就有一半的血液\N是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉如果落到\N邪恶的妖怪手中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的妖力就会越来越增强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你利用它的力量\N来变成人类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那颗玉就会得到净化\N就可能会就此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是四魂之玉的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉如果不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将变成一个普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  我愿意变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有丝毫的迟疑犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N你也要成为一个普通的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了\N不用再多说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知道  还问这种傻问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天中午
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西边森林的神木前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带着四魂之玉过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能让你称心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太期待  没耐心等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能现在就把我变成人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要无理取闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道夜晚\N四处充满了邪恶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用四魂之玉的话\N得等太阳升起来之后才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:12:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N天亮之后要马上进行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还很早  你继续睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  你不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐只是去\N帮你采些药草回来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药草这里不是已经有很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想也许还有更有效的药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐再去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫  你的眼睛还会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  今天好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么\N那时候的我觉得特别空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里很希望姐姐能留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她今天不要去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我强烈地这么祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉这家伙\N是不是睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你用这个来化妆\N你的本性也不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这口红根本就不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该用妖怪的血\N来妆点妆点就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从头到尾从来没有半点\N想成为人类的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉\N我就不客气的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗玉还得吸收\N更多仇恨的鲜血才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把村里的人都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一开始\N就打算欺骗我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句话也是谎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有丝毫的迟疑犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意变成人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到那个半妖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出现啦  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗  你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你半妖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那双难看的狗耳朵\N难道听不见我说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能\N把四魂之玉交给你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在这里一决生死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想跑  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉\N就会因为憎恶和仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而受到污染
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  你是骗我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想利用我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就报上名来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来\N我以后就不再叫你半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这样说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么现在又…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:17:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这个\N我就可以成为真正的妖怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就再也不会有人\N敢叫我半妖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉费我这么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉费我是这么信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来都没有\N怀疑过你的用心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你却… 可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  桔梗姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤的好重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你怎么会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我就这样死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要再多说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算最后变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听好  小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这颗四魂之玉\N跟我的尸体一起烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要让它\N再落入邪恶之徒的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把它\N一起带到那个世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后过了五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N一直被封印在神木上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N还是那个时候的老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就已经知道自己的生命\N到了尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此\N为什么没有射出破魔之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是射出了封印之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在这一棵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说能超越时间的\N时代树神木上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把犬夜叉封印起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N仇恨姐姐失去四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且被封印在\N神木上的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又流露出\N如此安详平静的面容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来我还是想不通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N是不是能够有明白的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第一个孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是可爱的女孩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不哭  不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字叫戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你朋友打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预习的笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我今天会带去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
